---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Servicios | Dakodev Software Solutions">
	<main class="pt-32 pb-20 relative z-10">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mb-16">
                <div class="text-accent-cyan font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-4">Especialización</div>
				<h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
					Nuestras <span class="text-gradient">Verticales</span>
				</h1>
				<p class="text-gray-400 text-lg leading-relaxed">
					Simplificamos lo complejo. Desde la presencia digital hasta el núcleo operativo de tu empresa, nuestras soluciones están diseñadas para escalar.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
				<!-- DAKO・WEB -->
				<div class="glass p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 hover:border-accent-cyan/50 transition-all duration-500 group relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-3 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity">
                        <span class="text-9xl font-black text-accent-cyan leading-none -mr-4 -mt-4">W</span>
                    </div>
                    
					<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent-cyan/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-7 h-7 text-accent-cyan" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					
                    <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mb-2">DAKO・WEB</h3>
                    <p class="text-accent-cyan font-medium text-sm mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider">Velocidad y Visibilidad</p>
                    
					<p class="text-gray-400 mb-8 border-b border-white/10 pb-6 min-h-[80px]">
						Tu carta de presentación digital: instantánea, segura y diseñada para vender desde el primer pixel.
					</p>
                    
                    <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-300">
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <span class="text-accent-cyan mr-2">✓</span>
                            <span><strong>Velocidad Extrema:</strong> Carga instantánea y SEO optimizado.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <span class="text-accent-cyan mr-2">✓</span>
                            <span><strong>Diseño Pixel-Perfect:</strong> Estética moderna adaptable a cualquier dispositivo.</span>
                        </li>
                         <li class="flex items-start">
                            <span class="text-accent-cyan mr-2">✓</span>
                            <span><strong>Seguridad Total:</strong> Disponibilidad 24/7 sin caídas.</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
				</div>

				<!-- DAKO・CORE -->
				<div class="glass p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 hover:border-accent-blue/50 transition-all duration-500 group relative overflow-hidden">
                     <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-3 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity">
                        <span class="text-9xl font-black text-accent-blue leading-none -mr-4 -mt-4">C</span>
                    </div>
                    
					<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent-blue/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-7 h-7 text-accent-blue" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					
                    <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mb-2">DAKO・CORE</h3>
                    <p class="text-accent-blue font-medium text-sm mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider">Control y Orden (ERP)</p>
                    
					<p class="text-gray-400 mb-8 border-b border-white/10 pb-6 min-h-[80px]">
						Deja el Excel. Toma el control total de ventas, inventario y facturación en un solo lugar centralizado.
					</p>
                    
                    <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-300">
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <span class="text-accent-blue mr-2">✓</span>
                            <span><strong>Todo en Uno:</strong> Ventas, Compras, Stock y CRM integrados.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <span class="text-accent-blue mr-2">✓</span>
                            <span><strong>Datos Real-Time:</strong> Tu empresa bajo control desde cualquier lugar.</span>
                        </li>
                         <li class="flex items-start">
                            <span class="text-accent-blue mr-2">✓</span>
                            <span><strong>Automatización:</strong> Facturación y gestión de stock automática.</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
				</div>

				<!-- DAKO・HYBRID -->
				<div class="glass p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 hover:border-accent-teal/50 transition-all duration-500 group relative overflow-hidden">
                     <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-3 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity">
                        <span class="text-9xl font-black text-accent-teal leading-none -mr-4 -mt-4">H</span>
                    </div>
                    
					<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent-teal/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-7 h-7 text-accent-teal" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 3.055A9.001 9.001 0 1020.945 13H11V3.055z" />
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20.488 9H15V3.512A9.025 9.025 0 0120.488 9z" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					
                    <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mb-2">DAKO・HYBRID</h3>
                    <p class="text-accent-teal font-medium text-sm mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider">Exclusividad y Experiencia</p>
                    
					<p class="text-gray-400 mb-8 border-b border-white/10 pb-6 min-h-[80px]">
						Software exclusivo diseñado para tu lógica de negocio. Portales de cliente y sistemas a medida.
					</p>
                    
                    <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-300">
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <span class="text-accent-teal mr-2">✓</span>
                            <span><strong>Portales Interactivos:</strong> Autogestión para tus clientes.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <span class="text-accent-teal mr-2">✓</span>
                            <span><strong>UX Premium:</strong> Interfaces modernas tipo App.</span>
                        </li>
                         <li class="flex items-start">
                            <span class="text-accent-teal mr-2">✓</span>
                            <span><strong>Conexión Total:</strong> Integración web + sistema interno.</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
				</div>
			</div>
            
            <div class="mt-20 text-center">
                <a href="/contacto/" class="px-8 py-4 bg-accent-cyan text-dark font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg shadow-accent-cyan/20 inline-flex items-center">
                    Solicitar Asesoría
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                </a>
            </div>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>
